<p>The food, cooked by the host, promises to be delicious! It’s a BYOT but instead of Tequila we are bringing wine. A bottle of Mexican wine. <strong>L.A Cetto</strong>, a <strong>2000 Estate Bottled Zinfande</strong>l from Valle De Guadalupe, Baja California. <br /> </p>

